      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg rend="center" type="letterhead"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00089-A-00001-000-00045-R"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals">Felix Salten</hi></hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50"><hi rend="capitals">Wien</hi></rs>,</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print">»<rs type="org" ref="#pmb29207">Berliner Neueste
                        Nachrichten</rs>.«</hi></seg></seg><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb199347">IX., Hörlgasse 16</rs>.</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print">»<rs type="org" ref="#pmb29664">Münchener
                        General-Anzeiger</rs>.«</hi></seg></seg></opener><p><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00089-A-00001-000-00045-V"/>Bitte sehr, wenn Sie <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03144-1"/><date when="1894-09-06">heute</date> noch <rs type="place" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb50">hieher</rs> kommen<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03144-1">Vermutlich wusste <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2167">Salten</rs> nicht, dass <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> bereits am <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1894-09-04" subtype="date-only"/> aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb213">Ischl</rs> zurückgekehrt war.</note>, so kommen Sie
                  <hi rend="underline" n="1">besti<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>t</hi> auf einen
               Sprung in’s 
               <rs type="place" ref="#pmb34210">Café Wortner</rs> (<rs type="place" ref="#pmb34210">Kaiserhof</rs>)</p><p>Ich muss Sie notwendig sprechen</p><closer>Ihr <lb/><signed>Salten</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
